        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-neutral-900 mb-8">
            About Me
        </h1>

        <div class="prose prose-neutral max-w-none prose-lg">
            <p>
                Hello! I'm CK-TOM, a software engineer with a passion for
                building clean, efficient, and user-friendly applications.
            </p>
            <p>
                My journey began with a curiosity for how things work under the
