                dabbling in systems programming and design.
            </p>
            <p>
                When I'm not coding, you can find me [insert hobbies here],
                reading tech blogs, or contributing to open source projects.
            </p>

            <h2>Experience</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <strong>Senior Engineer at Tech Corp</strong> (2022 - Present)
                    - Leading frontend architecture and team mentoring.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Full Stack Developer at Startup Inc</strong> (2019 - 2022)
                    - Built MVP and scaled application to 100k users.
                </li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Tech Stack</h2>
