                I work with a variety of tools, but my current favorites
                include:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Languages:</strong> TypeScript, Rust, Python</li>
                <li><strong>Frontend:</strong> React, Astro, Tailwind CSS</li>
                <li><strong>Backend:</strong> Node.js, PostgreSQL, Docker</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
